### Point of Sale Management API Tests
### Requires: Admin authentication
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5056/api
@contentType = application/json

### Get All Points of Sale
GET {{baseUrl}}/point-of-sales

### Get Point of Sale by ID
@posId = replace-with-actual-id
GET {{baseUrl}}/point-of-sales/{{posId}}

### Create Point of Sale
POST {{baseUrl}}/point-of-sales
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Tienda Centro",
  "code": "CENTRO-001",
  "address": "Calle Principal 123, Madrid",
  "phone": "+34 600 123 456",
  "email": "centro@test.com"
}

